abstract: >-
  A Claude Code skill that operationalizes the working tools of 51 books on
  judgment, reasoning, creativity, systems, uncertainty, models, and the
  philosophy of science. Ships with a three-round blind evaluation harness
  and full transcripts, including a documented negative result on scaling
  reference material from 21 to 51 books.
